column1: Escape the city and soak up the magic of the Whitsundays onboard our adventurous Bullet experience!
The perfect adventure to celebrate any birthdays or special events amongst the island wonder of the Whitsundays!
Explore the splendid nature of Whitehaven Beach and Hill Inlet Lookout.
Dive in and snorkel through the spectacular underwater ecosystems with access to some of the best spots in the Great Barrier Reef.
Jump aboard Bullet for a smooth and speedy ride, maximising your time for island exploration!

offers you a chance to explore the amazing natural beauty of the Whitsundays during your own personalised tour. Bullet can take up to 37 passengers at a time, and departs every day of the week, allowing for larger groups to explore the Whitsundays together at any time! Bullet offers more than any other day tour with fast cruising, snorkelling, a buffet lunch, a visit to Whitehaven Beach, a stop at Hill Inlet Lookout and the use of stand-up paddleboards. Take along your family, friends, or colleagues for the ultimate day of exploring all the Whitsundays has to offer.

Hop aboard Whitsunday Pearl for a luxurious sailing experience in the Whitsundays!
Visit Whitsunday icons such as Whitehaven Beach and Hill Inlet Lookout
Four private double cabins with ensuites
Sail through the Whitsunday Islands and snorkel the Great Barrier Reef
The perfect sailing tour for couples or intimate groups seeking luxury!
Picture this: you’re relaxing on the deck of a catamaran yacht while sailing through serene islandscapes. If this sounds like your tropical dream, the

is waiting to enchant you. With an intimate capacity for just 10 guests, an experienced crew onboard, visits to Whitsunday hidden gems and a decadent menu, Whitsunday Pearl is your exquisite home away from home. Spend three days lapping up the Whitsunday sunshine while exploring the region’s best. Stroll down the pristine Whitehaven Beach, visit Hill Inlet Lookout, and snorkel through the Great Barrier Reef Marine Park. Luxe island life beckons with Whitsunday Pearl, so let the vacation begin!

Indulge in the pristine, tropical waters of the Whitsunday Islands onboard the exclusive Whitsundays Adventurer Private Charter, destined to meet your every desire through a luxurious and personalised itinerary.
Experience an authentic, customised sailing tour directed by your professional skipper and host onboard the Whitsundays Adventurer!
Spend your days roaming the world-famous destinations of the Whitsunday Islands, followed by picturesque downtime in the heated foredeck spa.
Explore the surrounding aquatic playground through onboard activities such as snorkelling and stand-up paddleboarding!
An opportunity for families, friends, couples and small groups to skip the large crowds and unwind at their own pace.

Whitsunday Adventurer’s private charter is the perfect place to enjoy the beautiful Whitsundays with your dearest friends and loved ones. Your group will have the luxury of a personalised itinerary, taking time to relax, snorkel, swim and sunbathe, as well as explore the infamous Whitehaven Beach.

there is always a way for everyone to have fun! Dive down and snorkel amongst astounding fringing reefs, view the colourful coral from above on a stand-up paddleboard, or simply enjoy blissful downtime on the beautiful Whitehaven Beach. Enjoy your nights unwinding in the luxury onboard spa, or socialising with other guests –  Whitsunday Adventurer has it all! Relax and enjoy the world’s best scenery in comfort and style as your friendly and experienced crew takes care of everything. Whitsunday Adventurer is a dream escape for all types of travellers, including families, solo travellers, couples and groups of friends!

Hop on board the Whitsunday Adventurer, for an ultimate 3 day 3 night immersion in the Whitsunday Islands! This journey has something for everyone, ensuring the whole group has a great time! Have a go at snorkelling or stand-up paddleboarding to explore coral reefs, take a guided hike up to Hill Inlet Lookout and marvel at the swirling silica sands and turquoise waters below, walk along the vast stretch of South Whitehaven Beach, or simply unwind and relax with a soak in the onboard front deck spa to end a stunning day. Savour a cold bevvy and delicious dinner as the sunsets all while in the company of fellow travellers. It’s the perfect trip to do as much or as little as you like with experienced crew taking care of all the details!
